                     <summary>The <persName role="fmo" key="person_49996676"
                        ref="https://viaf.org/viaf/49996676/">1st Earl of Munster</persName>'s arms on the spine.</summary>
                     <seal type="stamp" subtype="armorial"><p>Blocked in <material>gold</material> on a skiver <material>leather</material> label adhered to the upper panel of the spine, features <heraldry>a crest with a chapeau turned up ermine a lion statant gardant crowned with a ducal coronet and gorged with a collar charged with three anchors and motto <q xml:lang="lt">Motto NEC TEMERE NEC TIMIDE</q> surmounted by a coronet</heraldry>.</p>
                        <decoNote type="stamp" subtype="dimensions"><p><dimensions type="arms" unit="mm">
                           <!-- check dims -->
                           <height>24</height>
                           <width>13</width></dimensions></p></decoNote>
                     </seal>
